sql:
SELECT title
FROM plots
WHERE plot_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Newest plots refer to the plots generated most recently based on the plot_date column; 
- Researcher 1 refers to the researcher with ID 1 in the researcher_id column; 
- Project name refers to the name of the project in the projects table.

